document_data.name: High Harvest Home
document_data.mainbody:
The '''High Harvest Home''' was a temple to [[Chauntea]], the Grain Goddess, situated in the city of [[Elturel]] in the [[Western Heartlands]] in the midâ€“14{{th}} century [[DR]].

''Circa'' [[1358 DR]] and through [[1367 DR]], it was managed by High Priest and Harvestmaster [[Raulauvin Oregh]], with eighteen priests and forty-two followers.

It provided aid and shelter to the faithful.
